decks.notes: The deck focuses on using Underworld Breach and Lotus Field to quickly cycle through the deck and generate mana. It utilizes a variety of cantrips and manipulation spells to find key pieces of the combo, while also using Wishclaw Talisman as a tutor engine. The main win condition is either casting Thassa's Oracle or Ad Nauseam to win the game on the spot. The deck aims to assemble its combo pieces as quickly as possible to outpace opponents and win the game in a single explosive turn.
